  <div class="badge-legend-row"><strong>Capabilities:</strong> <Badge text="tool" variant="success" /> function calling · <Badge text="reasoning" variant="success" /> thinking mode · <Badge text="multimodal" variant="success" /> image / video / audio inputs · <Badge text="research" variant="tip" /> active research workload (slower removal)</div>
